  "title": "Pirkei Avot §avot_03_10: He used to say: one with whom men are pleased, God is pleased.",
  "body": "He used to say: one with whom men are pleased, God is pleased. But anyone from whom men are displeased, God is displeased. Rabbi Dosa ben Harkinas said: morning sleep, midday wine, children’s talk and sitting in the assemblies of the ignorant put a man out of the world.",
